column4: "Tracks 16 & 17 are extra-tracks from the remixes of Death Of A Party by William Orbit (available on the album ""Bustin'+Dronin'""). They include a drums & percussion part and a synth bass riff. \012"

column5: just increase their volume and set the remix drums track to channel 10. (I suggest to mute the standard drums track whilst listening to the other one.)\012"
